{"tid":1564972,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"((突發)）【Yahoo民調又黎料】美國人權與民主發案","createTime":"2019-09-13T03:24:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T03:40:56.000Z","uid":278414,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"367e483c0474feb07895e0bff982d7ba80424e82","tid":1564972,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T03:24:52.000Z","msg":"Yahoo民調又黎料<br />\n各位手足 按一下唔會麻煩你好多時間<br />\n之後再廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（P牌推唔到 麻煩幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/poll/dc55ea70-d449-11e9-8292-338fe82ece59?guccounter=1&amp;guce_referrer=aHR0cHM6Ly9sb2dpbi55YWhvby5jb20v&amp;guce_referrer_sig=AQAAAEtaO6YSp3dI5-0lFrraqx9_TVA0QbJ6pAaVhPeoCox_2mGzjjuP_uE2NyuNL0r2oqBn4NZfrHg1WoALE8DqKo1-OZ2-s1MTmsB5ZRDPEPsuOgWXaLMRBMhpf9JJoaQz6su0zAllodn-w4fCoUOjwhjhl6Rim6g5Eeu4xQCCyPpH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fpoll%2Fdc55ea70-d449-11e9-8292-338fe82ece59%3Fguccounter%3D1%26guce_referrer%3DaHR0cHM6Ly9sb2dpbi55YWhvby5jb20v%26guce_referrer_sig%3DAQAAAEtaO6YSp3dI5-0lFrraqx9_TVA0QbJ6pAaVhPeoCox_2mGzjjuP_uE2NyuNL0r2oqBn4NZfrHg1WoALE8DqKo1-OZ2-s1MTmsB5ZRDPEPsuOgWXaLMRBMhpf9JJoaQz6su0zAllodn-w4fCoUOjwhjhl6Rim6g5Eeu4xQCCyPpH&d=m%2FBV6vIUiVByATU953YnmMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=27b9c449\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/poll/dc55ea70-d449-11e9-8292-338fe82ece59?guccounter=1&amp;guce_referrer=aHR0cHM6Ly9sb2dpbi55YWhvby5jb20v&amp;guce_referrer_sig=AQAAAEtaO6YSp3dI5-0lFrraqx9_TVA0QbJ6pAaVhPeoCox_2mGzjjuP_uE2NyuNL0r2oqBn4NZfrHg1WoALE8DqKo1-OZ2-s1MTmsB5ZRDPEPsuOgWXaLMRBMhpf9JJoaQz6su0zAllodn-w4fCoUOjwhjhl6Rim6g5Eeu4xQCCyPpH</a>"},{"pid":"ab82808e64b740e891c55babc395d2723465e71e","tid":1564972,"uid":157037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2